image_analysis.description: A photograph of a luxurious bathroom interior featuring black marble walls with white veining. The image shows a glass-enclosed shower or steam room area with a brass or gold-toned metal frame. A patterned robe (purple, gold, and green) hangs on the inside of the glass door. To the left, a vanity with a matching black marble top and brass legs is partially visible, along with a vertical light fixture with multiple bulbs. A blue towel is draped over a chrome towel rack in the foreground right, and another blue towel is visible on the left. A grey bath mat is on the floor.
